1125
00:42:21,026 --> 00:42:22,265
I've approached several banks

1126
00:42:22,745 --> 00:42:23,705
about loans.

1127
00:42:24,145 --> 00:42:25,906
With Yan Studio's current scale,

1128
00:42:26,705 --> 00:42:28,105
