1129
00:42:29,866 --> 00:42:30,346
Really?

1130
00:42:30,625 --> 00:42:31,346
Chill.

1131
00:42:32,346 --> 00:42:32,986
Let's see.

1132
00:42:33,225 --> 00:42:33,986
We'll work on it

1133
00:42:34,026 --> 00:42:35,026
